display_long_description:
# UNLEASH THE ORDNANCE WITH A PINCH OF YOUR FINGERS
Your city is under attack! Deploy the command console to manage your defenses and protect your citizens. Thwart enemy attacks with carefully timed retaliatory strikes!

[media]

# IMPROVE YOUR REFLEXES & MASTER THE ARSENAL
If you survive the immediate onslaught, you'll get a chance to rebuild your city or upgrade your arsenal from a selection of missiles, bombs, drones and lasers. Complete contracts to earn extra score!

[media]

# COMPETE WITH FRIENDS ON THE LEADERBOARDS
With each wave, new threats emerge: faster missiles, helicopters, drunken kamikaze... Will you achieve eternal glory on the leaderboards, or will your city fall under siege?

[media]

# RETRO ARCADE ACTION MEETS MODERN MIXED REALITY MAYHEM
Whether you're hanging out in the living room, catching a sunset outside, stuck in the toilet, or anywhere else, you can always quickly jump into the action!

[media]

**"A must-have for Quest"** - UploadVR 🎖️

**"Breathes new life into an old game"** - MIXED News 🎖️

**"Gets your adrenaline pumping"** - 6DOF Reviews 🎖️

**"Greater than my imagination"** - Bill Carlton, arcade gaming legend 🎖️

# KEY FEATURES
- 6 **Training** Maps; 7 **Practice** Maps; 2 **Arcade** Maps with **Leaderboards**
- 8 Turret types, 5 Enemy types
- 15 Turret Contracts (i.e. skill challenges/bounties)
- And more still in development...

Join the community:
**notsuspicious.biz/discord**
